{"tid":1092551,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[直播] 清明放假 渣渣地同幾個巴絲行哂成條電車路","createTime":"2019-04-05T02:36:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T19:00:52.000Z","uid":62752,"like":48,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"db040ff94f0211f9fe35971074127570e6f63cc5","tid":1092551,"uid":62752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:36:49.000Z","msg":"見今日紅日 就約左幾個唔洗拜山嘅巴絲一齊行哂成條電車路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實都唔係話好長, 但多人嘛, <br />\n渣渣地打算慢慢行<br />\n順便睇下幾個都好似幾出名嘅地方<br />\n咩大館呀, 海山樓咁<br />\n順便又睇下有咩好食, 行過路過食下好西咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老老實實, 我呢D一直住養牛地方既毒拎就真係十年都唔去一次港島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次黎個初探 <br />\n<br />\n呢個就係電車路MAP, 今次我地行東行線<br />\n由堅尼地城行到去筲箕灣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j097mCK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj097mCK.jpg&h=330d30f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBTW 其實之前都行過一轉, 由元朗行路去大埔林村拋寶牒<br />\n回帶：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1023659/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1023659/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n希望今次都可以無驚無險順利完成啦!!<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zy6EXfH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzy6EXfH.jpg&h=734e6ae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同架車目的地一樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n準備出發，而家10點鬆啲，目標係5點前會行到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n感動既係, 大家都無飛機, 如果咁多位巴絲有咩好西/景點推介既, 我地都睇下係咪可以食到OR去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6260887e93fc061c1afa0d3f58635e9e58a440c6","tid":1092551,"uid":243550,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:41:18.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"846b17dc56bedff3c3ce2370f3680ee17bc57c7e","tid":1092551,"uid":62752,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:41:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xBXkGPS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxBXkGPS.png&h=b0dba151&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲同大家食左個好似好勁既冰室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a22802bd8110d68190d7fc106eef3944de934d7","tid":1092551,"uid":84284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:56:00.000Z","msg":"LM <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 試過由一邊搭到另一邊 無試過咁行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1407c3c9606b8388782243b8a5e5977b08883e0","tid":1092551,"uid":62752,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"9a22802bd8110d68190d7fc106eef3944de934d7","tid":1092551,"uid":84284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:56:00.000Z","msg":"LM <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 試過由一邊搭到另一邊 無試過咁行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:57:09.000Z","msg":"可能行快過搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9940e41e1c9d5f1a075f77ff95ada925179ec8c9","tid":1092551,"uid":62752,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy