,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T08:56:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KZCwQzH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKZCwQzH.png&h=4cb07e98&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iz0ncN3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fiz0ncN3.png&h=bb4a6e4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n終於到西灣河啦，買d 小食食下先"},{"pid":"6da69fa2abb2c61fe25073659321ee61d8614cc2","tid":1092551,"uid":62752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T09:11:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lh0VxS1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLh0VxS1.png&h=749b1976&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wpFVxS2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwpFVxS2.png&h=3b89306f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雞蛋仔已試。"},{"pid":"a9c5dec83db4d78db1b7bdcf3e295212effcab03","tid":1092551,"uid":108756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T09:19:08.000Z","msg":"見過咁多個行路post好多我都覺得勁<br />\n唯獨呢個 可能因為住港島個陣成日都咁樣行西行到東 所以覺得無咩野<br />\n不過見你地唔係住港島都咁有雅興咁做 支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9db7fcdaeda9766e4e2f9f86b6e2adc41b939e1","tid":1092551,"uid":62752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9c5dec83db4d78db1b7bdcf3e295212effcab03","tid":1092551,"uid":108756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T09:19:08.000Z","msg":"見過咁多個行路post好多我都覺得勁<br />\n唯獨呢個 可能因為住港島個陣成日都咁樣行西行到東 所以覺得無咩野<br />\n不過見你地唔係住港島都咁有雅興咁做 支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T09:27:45.000Z","msg":"為左飲飲食食o者，長度唔係重點。"},{"pid":"b21a6431b517aa68e002281a0abbc46e9cbd8dec","tid":1092551,"uid":62752,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T10:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0uVqVu7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0uVqVu7.jpg&h=346f67d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/henprBL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhenprBL.jpg&h=ba4d08e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地17:45 左右到左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲左啲 中途啲巴絲打係咁飲飲食食 所以慢左少少<br />\n<br />\n影完相太興奮<br />\n唔記得update<br />\n我地又去左地鐵站附近再食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n感動既係 平時無咩郁動既大家 全部都完成到<br />\n有巴絲分享見到啲平時無咩留意既小店<br />\n又去左啲聽過好耐但從未去過既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔係一班人一齊行 應該會坐車走左去<br />\n<br />\n雖然真係渣渣地，但我地幾個都唔係住港島既巴絲，對港島認識又多左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日唔洗留係屋企hea過 都係開心事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 都多謝咁多位連登巴絲陪我地去行 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9393731a04d14a9c6f5e9c5bf3475acbee978ec5","tid":1092551,"uid":35301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T10:34:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d964a1ed3c6b43d0175872a4299aeffec1d905d6","tid":1092551,"uid":171098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a5363a0f239e606f42c859d0e77702c2494dc03","tid":1092551,"uid":62752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"777fd1b6246d475f865540a24aa6f1b7f626934b","tid":1092551,"uid":171098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T07:59:37.000Z","msg":"點Join<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" cl